snippet.title: Wiz - Melbourne House Commodore 64 gameplay
snippet.description:
Started out well, wandered round for a bit...and then the usual 'I can't be bothered to design game screens properly' curse of a powerful wizard who can cast spells not being able to walk round a tree

FFS!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Not too bad otherwise :o)
